== Template:TutorialInfo ==

This template displays tutorial metadata in a consistent format.

=== Usage ===

<pre>
{{TutorialInfo
|level=Beginner/Intermediate/Advanced/Expert
|duration=30 minutes
|prerequisites=[[Getting Started]], [[Basic Git]]
|topics=Branches, Commits, Pull Requests
}}
</pre>

=== Parameters ===

* '''level''' - Tutorial difficulty level (Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced, Expert)
* '''duration''' - Estimated time to complete
* '''prerequisites''' - Required knowledge or completed tutorials
* '''topics''' - Main topics covered in the tutorial

=== Example ===

{{TutorialInfo
|level=Intermediate
|duration=45 minutes
|prerequisites=[[Getting Started with GitHub]]
|topics=GitHub Actions, CI/CD, Automation
}}

